### US-009: Breadcrumb Navigation
**Priority:** 2
**Maven Steps:** [5, 10]
**MCP Tools:** []

As a documentation reader, I want breadcrumbs so that I can navigate back up the hierarchy.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
